    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a bulletproofed dual-VANOS system. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The suspension maintains factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and longitudinal stability these chassis are renowned for. A mechanically flawless, turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
