      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that presents in showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, shielded from the elements and treated with an obsessive level of care. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring original paint with a deep, mirror-like luster and absolutely no chips, dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the interior remains pristine; the upholstery is supple and shows zero signs of wear, the dash is perfect, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the smallest interior light, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians, with a complete binder of service records included. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule example of automotive excellence. Serious inquiries only; inspections are encouraged to appreciate the unrivaled quality of this specimen.",
